HEADWORD: Phylum
<hw>Phy"lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Phyla</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Phylon</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of the
